297
00:14:22,900 --> 00:14:23,610
Hold on.

298
00:14:25,660 --> 00:14:26,570
Let's go.

299
00:14:29,060 --> 00:14:29,850
This is good.

300
00:14:45,780 --> 00:14:46,850
Go through it again.

301
00:14:47,210 --> 00:14:47,660
Okay.

302
00:14:55,450 --> 00:14:57,060
Qinglai, what are you doing?

303
00:14:57,690 --> 00:14:58,420
Hey, Mr. Guan.

304
00:14:59,300 --> 00:15:00,140
I picked up a pot of plants.

305
00:15:00,690 --> 00:15:01,450
I'm fixing it.

306
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:05,260
Oh, right.

307
00:15:06,090 --> 00:15:07,090
Do I have a post?

308
00:15:07,730 --> 00:15:09,180
The client said it was delivered.

309
00:15:10,570 --> 00:15:11,610
Yes, there's one.

310
00:15:18,380 --> 00:15:18,900
Here.

311
00:15:21,850 --> 00:15:23,210
Qinglai, remember,

312
00:15:23,570 --> 00:15:24,450
whenever there's a post,

313
00:15:24,450 --> 00:15:25,690
pass it to me instantly.

314
00:15:25,690 --> 00:15:26,570
Lest it's something important.

315
00:15:26,940 --> 00:15:28,090
You weren't here,

316
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:30,140
so I just left it in the storeroom.

317
00:15:30,610 --> 00:15:31,380
Then I forgot about it.

318
00:15:32,380 --> 00:15:32,970
Sorry.

319
00:15:36,330 --> 00:15:37,490
Leave it at the reception next time.

320
00:15:38,300 --> 00:15:38,940
Okay.

321
00:15:41,450 --> 00:15:42,090
Besides,

322
00:15:42,660 --> 00:15:43,810
can you not

323
00:15:44,090 --> 00:15:44,970
do this here?

324
00:15:45,300 --> 00:15:46,450
The coffee table is full of dirt.

325
00:15:46,730 --> 00:15:47,690
What if a client

326
00:15:47,940 --> 00:15:49,450
walks in and sees it?

327
00:15:49,940 --> 00:15:51,330
It's okay. I'm going to tidy up.

328
00:15:51,330 --> 00:15:52,420
I'll clean it up soon.

329
00:15:52,940 --> 00:15:53,490
Very soon.

330
00:16:21,940 --> 00:16:22,460
This...

331
00:16:22,850 --> 00:16:23,250
Wow.

332
00:16:23,820 --> 00:16:25,530
Isn't this the pot of plant
you picked up by the roadside?

333
00:16:25,730 --> 00:16:26,130
Yes.

334
00:16:26,980 --> 00:16:27,730
How do you like it?

335
00:16:28,610 --> 00:16:30,100
You fixed the pot.

336
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:32,220
That's amazing.

337
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:34,490
It's just fixing the pot. No big deal.

338
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:36,490
Let's place it here.

339
00:16:40,530 --> 00:16:41,980
Whose flower is this?

340
00:16:42,580 --> 00:16:43,580
It looks good.

341
00:16:44,060 --> 00:16:44,980
He did it.

342
00:16:46,300 --> 00:16:47,370
Why is it placed here?

343
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:49,100
It looks better on my table.

344
00:16:50,730 --> 00:16:52,060
It looks good here.

345
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:53,460
Whoever comes in can see it.

346
00:16:54,490 --> 00:16:55,250
Qinglai.

347
00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:57,490
Are you trying

348
00:16:57,580 --> 00:16:58,940
to impress Xingfu?

349
00:17:01,530 --> 00:17:02,100
This...

350
00:17:03,980 --> 00:17:05,900
Isn't this the pot of flower you fixed?

351
00:17:06,380 --> 00:17:06,770
Yes.

352
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:08,420
Do you like this kind of work?

353
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:10,380
Yes.

354
00:17:10,660 --> 00:17:12,330
Then don't waste your talent.

355
00:17:12,980 --> 00:17:14,490
Get some money from the accountant later.

356
00:17:14,570 --> 00:17:15,330
I'll approve of it.

357
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:17,330
Decorate the firm.

358
00:17:17,940 --> 00:17:19,140
Having some plants make

359
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:20,330
the place look lively.

360
00:17:21,460 --> 00:17:22,090
Okay.

361
00:17:22,220 --> 00:17:23,140
But the premise

362
00:17:23,570 --> 00:17:24,770
is not to have dirt everywhere.

363
00:17:25,860 --> 00:17:26,700
Sure thing.

364
00:17:30,620 --> 00:17:31,290
Do you like it?

365
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:33,660
What? Get back to work.

366
00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:34,570
Okay.

367
00:17:35,140 --> 00:17:35,530
Leave it.

368
00:17:35,530 --> 00:17:36,420
I'll place it here.

369
00:17:48,090 --> 00:17:48,730
Xingfu,

370
00:17:49,050 --> 00:17:50,380
are you opening a flower shop?

371
00:17:51,730 --> 00:17:52,860
Qinglai did it.

372
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:55,220
He once picked up a flower pot

373
00:17:55,220 --> 00:17:56,090
and it survived.

374
00:17:56,530 --> 00:17:57,620
After being encouraged

375
00:17:58,290 --> 00:17:58,980
by Guan Tao,

376
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:00,860
he turned the law firm into a garden.

377
00:18:01,490 --> 00:18:03,090
And then he turned this place into a garden.

378
00:18:04,330 --> 00:18:05,810
Whenever he has time,

379
00:18:05,900 --> 00:18:07,220
he either digs a bag of soil

380
00:18:07,460 --> 00:18:08,730
or looks for some plants.

381
00:18:09,010 --> 00:18:10,770
I told him to come home after work,

382
00:18:11,490 --> 00:18:14,140
yet he went to the park for more plants.

383
00:18:14,490 --> 00:18:15,460
Isn't this good?

384
00:18:15,770 --> 00:18:16,290
Think about it.

385
00:18:16,290 --> 00:18:18,290
Everyone has something he likes to do.

386
00:18:18,290 --> 00:18:20,180
Since he likes this, let him be.

387
00:18:21,010 --> 00:18:22,180
I'm not stopping him.

388
00:18:23,010 --> 00:18:23,900
Besides,

389
00:18:24,730 --> 00:18:26,050
ever since

390
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:27,420
he started growing these plants,

391
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:29,290
he became more spirited.

392
00:18:29,810 --> 00:18:31,380
He doesn't grumble anymore.

393
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:32,770
Isn't it great?

394
00:18:32,940 --> 00:18:33,420
Yes.

395
00:18:34,810 --> 00:18:35,770
I'm thinking

396
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:39,140
about opening a plant nursery for him.

397
00:18:39,570 --> 00:18:40,660
So he can work there.

398
00:18:41,700 --> 00:18:43,290
It must be better than working in a law firm.

399
00:18:43,860 --> 00:18:45,660
I think that's a good idea.

400
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:47,050
Qinglai

401
00:18:47,050 --> 00:18:49,220
likes to work

402
00:18:49,220 --> 00:18:50,090
with dirt and soil.

403
00:18:51,180 --> 00:18:51,980
I finally

404
00:18:52,290 --> 00:18:53,330
know Qinglai.

405
00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:55,140
He's indeed a countryman.

406
00:18:58,420 --> 00:19:00,010
You're gossiping about me again.

407
00:19:00,330 --> 00:19:02,460
How is it possible, Qinglai?

408
00:19:02,530 --> 00:19:04,530
What's in that bag?

409
00:19:08,530 --> 00:19:09,090
Soil.

410
00:19:15,220 --> 00:19:16,860
Wash your hands and eat.

411
00:19:21,250 --> 00:19:23,420
Stop taking plants from the park.

412
00:19:23,660 --> 00:19:24,900
That's public property.

413
00:19:26,380 --> 00:19:28,290
I was just pruning their branches.

414
00:19:28,980 --> 00:19:30,940
The plants don't grow well without pruning.

415
00:19:31,330 --> 00:19:33,180
The guard of the park, Du,

416
00:19:33,770 --> 00:19:34,940
is also a gardener.

417
00:19:35,250 --> 00:19:36,290
Every time I prune the plants,

418
00:19:36,290 --> 00:19:37,940
he serves me good tea and cigarette.

419
00:19:38,420 --> 00:19:39,730
Or else he would need to prune them.

420
00:19:39,860 --> 00:19:41,980
I'm helping him by pruning the plants.

421
00:19:42,530 --> 00:19:44,220
Don't talk nonsense if you don't understand.

422
00:19:45,140 --> 00:19:46,730
Okay, I don't understand.

423
00:19:46,900 --> 00:19:48,050
I'm wrong.

424
00:19:48,250 --> 00:19:50,010
Exactly. You don't know gardening

425
00:19:50,050 --> 00:19:51,530
as good as Qinglai.

426
00:19:51,530 --> 00:19:53,140
I don't know if he has other talents,

427
00:19:53,140 --> 00:19:54,730
but gardening is his expertise.

428
00:19:55,700 --> 00:19:57,050
Although they're lawyers,

429
00:19:57,490 --> 00:19:59,140
they have to ask me about plants.

430
00:19:59,810 --> 00:20:00,220
Do you know?

431
00:20:00,220 --> 00:20:02,140
They often ask me about their plants at home,

432
00:20:02,330 --> 00:20:03,250
which are badly planted.

433
00:20:03,730 --> 00:20:05,090
I don't ask for money for that.

434
00:20:06,050 --> 00:20:07,900
Qinglai is very popular in our firm.

435
00:20:08,290 --> 00:20:09,730
They even gave him a raise.

436
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:12,140
Awesome, Qinglai.

437
00:20:19,290 --> 00:20:19,900
Mr. Liu.

438
00:20:22,180 --> 00:20:22,900
I changed the soil

439
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:24,010
of your plants.

440
00:20:24,420 --> 00:20:26,050
Water it once a week.

441
00:20:26,530 --> 00:20:27,570
Don't water it like you used to.

442
00:20:28,570 --> 00:20:29,460
Okay, thank you.

443
00:20:29,460 --> 00:20:30,010
You're welcome.

444
00:20:35,420 --> 00:20:36,730
There's a spider.

445
00:20:37,490 --> 00:20:38,250
A red one.

446
00:20:38,570 --> 00:20:40,050
Let me do it.

447
00:20:40,050 --> 00:20:41,490
It's in the notebook.

448
00:20:44,490 --> 00:20:45,490
Okay, it's settled now.

449
00:20:46,420 --> 00:20:46,900
It's gone now.

450
00:20:47,180 --> 00:20:47,900
Qinglai.

451
00:20:48,290 --> 00:20:49,050
Ever since

452
00:20:49,050 --> 00:20:50,700
we have so many plants here,

453
00:20:51,050 --> 00:20:52,250
there have been a lot of insects.

454
00:20:52,250 --> 00:20:54,250
Can you spray some insecticide?

455
00:20:54,250 --> 00:20:54,810
Indeed.

456
00:20:55,090 --> 00:20:56,140
The plants can't be sprayed.

457
00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:57,380
Besides,

458
00:20:57,700 --> 00:20:59,220
an insecticide doesn't work universally.

459
00:20:59,290 --> 00:21:00,940
It can't be solved so easily.

460
00:21:01,570 --> 00:21:03,140
I think

461
00:21:03,460 --> 00:21:05,180
the plants look good from afar.

462
00:21:05,250 --> 00:21:06,050
When I get closer to them,

463
00:21:06,530 --> 00:21:07,730
they smell pungent.

464
00:21:08,090 --> 00:21:09,180
[Chief's office]
It's the fertilizer.

465
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:11,700
If you want the plants to look and smell good,

466
00:21:11,730 --> 00:21:12,810
you can't leave out the fertilizer.

467
00:21:13,290 --> 00:21:15,050
Besides, without the smell of fertilizer,

468
00:21:15,330 --> 00:21:16,660
the flowers won't be fragrant.

469
00:21:17,090 --> 00:21:17,770
You don't understand.

470
00:21:18,090 --> 00:21:18,900
Smell it, and see how fragrant it is.

471
00:21:19,180 --> 00:21:20,250
That's enough, Qinglai.

472
00:21:20,460 --> 00:21:20,730
That's enough.

473
00:21:20,730 --> 00:21:22,090
-It's fine.
-Don't you have work to do?

474
00:21:23,570 --> 00:21:24,140
Qinglai.

475
00:21:27,090 --> 00:21:27,660
Mr. Guan.

476
00:21:27,660 --> 00:21:28,730
I happened to be looking for you.

477
00:21:29,660 --> 00:21:30,570
This is the receipt

478
00:21:30,570 --> 00:21:32,250
for the fertilizers and pots I bought.

479
00:21:32,660 --> 00:21:33,420
Please sign it

480
00:21:33,420 --> 00:21:34,090
so I can reimburse it.

481
00:21:37,660 --> 00:21:38,050
Here.

482
00:21:43,220 --> 00:21:43,620
Thank you.

483
00:21:47,620 --> 00:21:48,220
Qinglai.

484
00:21:48,940 --> 00:21:50,490
It's good

485
00:21:50,570 --> 00:21:51,220
that you like plants.

486
00:21:51,330 --> 00:21:51,860
However,

487
00:21:52,860 --> 00:21:54,460
you shouldn't delay your regular work.

488
00:21:57,490 --> 00:21:57,810
Here.

489
00:21:57,810 --> 00:21:58,220
Okay.

490
00:22:01,530 --> 00:22:02,220
By the way,

491
00:22:02,810 --> 00:22:03,980
please send this out.

492
00:22:04,380 --> 00:22:05,980
Okay, I'll water the plants first.

493
00:22:06,180 --> 00:22:06,860
Then I'll send it.

494
00:22:08,180 --> 00:22:08,730
No, I...

495
00:22:14,290 --> 00:22:15,010
I'll send it.

496
00:22:16,770 --> 00:22:17,330
Xingfu.

497
00:22:19,220 --> 00:22:20,010
Come to see me

498
00:22:20,530 --> 00:22:21,330
when you're done.

499
00:22:22,700 --> 00:22:23,530
Okay.

500
00:22:30,290 --> 00:22:30,810
Thank you.

501
00:22:36,220 --> 00:22:36,940
Why did you hit me?

502
00:22:39,570 --> 00:22:40,460
Xingfu.

503
00:22:41,220 --> 00:22:42,490
You should talk to Qinglai.

504
00:22:42,810 --> 00:22:43,900
This can't go on this way.

505
00:22:44,220 --> 00:22:44,770
After all,

506
00:22:44,770 --> 00:22:46,570
he should do his job.

507
00:22:46,810 --> 00:22:48,980
He can't only be caring for the plants.

508
00:22:49,660 --> 00:22:52,460
Yes. You said it casually once,

509
00:22:52,810 --> 00:22:55,140
yet he's getting more and more into it.

510
00:22:56,570 --> 00:22:57,380
Mr. Guan.

511
00:22:58,570 --> 00:23:00,140
It's mainly because

512
00:23:00,290 --> 00:23:01,330
Qinglai has always

513
00:23:01,380 --> 00:23:03,530
liked to plant and farm.

514
00:23:03,770 --> 00:23:05,330
He's happy when he does these things.

515
00:23:06,420 --> 00:23:08,730
Things haven't been going well
in the city for him.

516
00:23:09,490 --> 00:23:10,940
Since he's happy,

517
00:23:11,010 --> 00:23:13,090
I didn't stop him.

518
00:23:13,530 --> 00:23:15,220
I can tell

519
00:23:15,290 --> 00:23:16,900
that he really likes

520
00:23:17,380 --> 00:23:19,180
to take care of those plants.

521
00:23:19,620 --> 00:23:21,250
But after all, this is a law firm,

522
00:23:21,250 --> 00:23:22,490
not a greenhouse.

523
00:23:22,900 --> 00:23:24,810
In the beginning, people found it interesting,

524
00:23:24,810 --> 00:23:26,250
they liked it,

525
00:23:26,380 --> 00:23:27,010
and were happy about it.

526
00:23:27,860 --> 00:23:28,730
But recently,

527
00:23:28,730 --> 00:23:30,290
Qinglai has been doing things wrong.

528
00:23:31,490 --> 00:23:33,530
He can't make gardening his main business

529
00:23:34,050 --> 00:23:36,570
and ignore his real job.

530
00:23:36,570 --> 00:23:37,700
This is not okay.

531
00:23:39,530 --> 00:23:41,980
I know he has his pride.

532
00:23:42,140 --> 00:23:44,090
He doesn't even want people here to know

533
00:23:44,660 --> 00:23:46,330
about your relationship.

534
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:47,490
I understand that.

535
00:23:48,330 --> 00:23:50,220
He doesn't want others to look down on him

536
00:23:50,220 --> 00:23:51,420
for making less money than you.

537
00:23:51,730 --> 00:23:52,220
Therefore,

538
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:54,180
I didn't tell anyone.

539
00:23:56,050 --> 00:23:57,050
But you saw it today,

540
00:23:57,730 --> 00:23:59,380
he didn't even take my order seriously.

541
00:24:00,700 --> 00:24:01,140
Yes.

542
00:24:01,140 --> 00:24:01,730
Besides,

543
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:03,940
you're the one
who has been buying lunch for him, right?

544
00:24:04,530 --> 00:24:06,460
He leaves on time

545
00:24:06,490 --> 00:24:07,290
during lunch break.

546
00:24:08,940 --> 00:24:09,660
I'm very sure

547
00:24:10,940 --> 00:24:12,380
that he's not in the law firm now.

548
00:24:16,250 --> 00:24:17,330
Mr. Guan.

549
00:24:17,530 --> 00:24:19,180
I'll keep an eye on him

550
00:24:19,570 --> 00:24:20,770
so he doesn't delay his work

551
00:24:21,530 --> 00:24:23,420
and put you in a difficult position.

552
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:26,900
Xingfu.

553
00:24:26,900 --> 00:24:28,010
You must understand me.

554
00:24:28,700 --> 00:24:29,900
We have more employees now.

555
00:24:30,290 --> 00:24:32,140
It's not the same
as when there were the four of us.

556
00:24:32,860 --> 00:24:34,570
If I allow him

557
00:24:34,860 --> 00:24:35,730
to work like this,

558
00:24:35,900 --> 00:24:37,010
how can I manage the others?

559
00:24:37,770 --> 00:24:38,660
Besides kindness,

560
00:24:38,940 --> 00:24:40,180
a team also requires

561
00:24:41,290 --> 00:24:42,090
discipline.

562
00:24:42,660 --> 00:24:44,180
Yes, I get it.

563
00:24:44,810 --> 00:24:46,140
I'll talk to him at home.

564
00:24:56,530 --> 00:24:57,330
Hello.

565
00:24:58,940 --> 00:24:59,250
Yes?

566
00:24:59,900 --> 00:25:00,530
I am.

567
00:25:02,810 --> 00:25:03,420
What?

568
00:25:05,180 --> 00:25:06,250
Okay, I'm coming.

569
00:25:08,010 --> 00:25:08,530
What's going on?

570
00:25:09,050 --> 00:25:11,010
Qinglai is arrested by the police.

571
00:25:23,700 --> 00:25:24,530
What happened?

572
00:25:25,140 --> 00:25:26,490
They insisted that I stole the plants.

573
00:25:27,330 --> 00:25:28,900
The pruning is good for the plants.

574
00:25:28,900 --> 00:25:30,180
The plants are still right there.

575
00:25:30,940 --> 00:25:31,770
I propagated

576
00:25:31,770 --> 00:25:32,860
the cut branches.

577
00:25:33,140 --> 00:25:34,180
Otherwise, they would have thrown them away.

578
00:25:34,620 --> 00:25:36,220
Isn't this a win-win situation?

579
00:25:36,730 --> 00:25:37,420
In the countryside,

580
00:25:37,420 --> 00:25:38,660
we could pluck any flowers.

581
00:25:38,660 --> 00:25:39,570
It's no big deal.

582
00:25:40,570 --> 00:25:42,530
Yet this is considered stealing in the city.

