00:25:47,140 --> 00:25:48,330
I told you many times

585
00:25:48,770 --> 00:25:49,730
to stop doing it.

586
00:25:50,330 --> 00:25:51,180
Are you happy now?

587
00:25:51,330 --> 00:25:52,660
They arrested you as a thief.

588
00:25:53,090 --> 00:25:54,380
Who's Wang Qinglai's family?

589
00:25:55,140 --> 00:25:56,380
Officer, I am.

590
00:25:56,810 --> 00:25:57,460
Who is this?

591
00:25:58,010 --> 00:25:58,940
Hello, officer.

592
00:25:59,900 --> 00:26:01,730
I'm Wang Qinglai's employer

593
00:26:01,730 --> 00:26:03,860
and his lawyer.

594
00:26:04,380 --> 00:26:05,810
May I know what happened?

595
00:26:06,490 --> 00:26:07,530
It wasn't a huge issue actually.

596
00:26:08,010 --> 00:26:10,090
He was cutting plants in the public garden.

597
00:26:10,700 --> 00:26:12,090
He also took away some branches.

598
00:26:12,090 --> 00:26:13,180
The guards found out.

599
00:26:13,570 --> 00:26:15,090
They started arguing and fighting.

600
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:17,660
We've mediated between them just now.

601
00:26:18,250 --> 00:26:19,180
By the way,

602
00:26:19,660 --> 00:26:21,050
pruning is a good thing.

603
00:26:21,460 --> 00:26:23,290
But taking away the cut branches

604
00:26:23,770 --> 00:26:25,090
can cause unnecessary suspicion.

605
00:26:25,700 --> 00:26:27,570
Please take him back to educate him.

606
00:26:28,090 --> 00:26:29,010
From what I heard,

607
00:26:29,620 --> 00:26:31,940
this isn't his first time doing this.

608
00:26:33,180 --> 00:26:34,460
Sorry, officer.

609
00:26:34,570 --> 00:26:35,490
Sorry for the trouble.

610
00:26:35,810 --> 00:26:36,330
It's okay.

611
00:26:37,090 --> 00:26:38,380
Please do the formalities outside

612
00:26:38,900 --> 00:26:39,620
and take him with you.

613
00:26:39,980 --> 00:26:40,620
Okay.

614
00:26:41,140 --> 00:26:42,010
I'll go through the formalities.

615
00:26:49,250 --> 00:26:49,900
Qinglai.

616
00:26:51,420 --> 00:26:53,290
Legally speaking,

617
00:26:54,810 --> 00:26:57,460
the plants in the public garden
are state property.

618
00:26:57,570 --> 00:26:59,330
No one can touch them without permission.

619
00:27:00,180 --> 00:27:01,810
Not to mention that you actually pruned them.

620
00:27:02,460 --> 00:27:03,770
You shouldn't have done this.

621
00:27:05,570 --> 00:27:06,700
In that case,

622
00:27:07,140 --> 00:27:08,090
many plants

623
00:27:08,090 --> 00:27:09,770
in the law firm were propagated by me.

624
00:27:11,090 --> 00:27:12,090
Does it mean that the law firm

625
00:27:13,220 --> 00:27:14,140
is a place to hide the stolen?

626
00:27:18,900 --> 00:27:19,860
I guess you are right

627
00:27:20,010 --> 00:27:20,770
if you must put it that way.

628
00:27:20,770 --> 00:27:21,490
However,

629
00:27:23,140 --> 00:27:24,420
it may not seem to be a big problem

630
00:27:24,490 --> 00:27:25,290
since they didn't pursue it further.

631
00:27:25,940 --> 00:27:27,460
[Police]
But if they were to hold you accountable,

632
00:27:27,490 --> 00:27:29,140
do you know what crime you committed?

633
00:27:30,660 --> 00:27:32,490
This is the theft of national property.

634
00:27:37,255 --> 00:27:43,675
[Public Security]

635
00:27:46,860 --> 00:27:47,250
You.

636
00:27:47,730 --> 00:27:48,620
Guan Tao helped us,

637
00:27:48,620 --> 00:27:49,700
yet you didn't thank him.

638
00:27:50,330 --> 00:27:51,090
Mr. Guan.

639
00:27:51,940 --> 00:27:52,900
I'm sorry

640
00:27:52,980 --> 00:27:53,940
for the trouble today.

641
00:27:54,250 --> 00:27:55,220
You're most welcome.

642
00:28:00,050 --> 00:28:00,980
Just go home

643
00:28:01,330 --> 00:28:02,050
instead of the office.

644
00:28:04,530 --> 00:28:05,180
Okay.

645
00:28:05,730 --> 00:28:06,290
Also, Xingfu,

646
00:28:09,180 --> 00:28:10,290
don't forget

647
00:28:12,180 --> 00:28:12,860
what I told you.

648
00:28:14,420 --> 00:28:15,940
You have an appointment
with Frank tomorrow at noon.

649
00:28:16,570 --> 00:28:17,220
Don't forget.

650
00:28:17,380 --> 00:28:17,860
I know.

651
00:28:18,770 --> 00:28:19,380
The car key.

652
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:27,490
Let's go.

653
00:28:39,660 --> 00:28:40,180
Morning, Xingfu.

654
00:28:40,180 --> 00:28:40,860
-Morning Xingfu.
-Good morning.

655
00:28:40,860 --> 00:28:41,700
[Fangyuan Law Firm]

656
00:28:42,700 --> 00:28:43,570
I heard Qinglai

657
00:28:43,570 --> 00:28:45,420
was arrested yesterday
for stealing national property.

658
00:28:45,770 --> 00:28:46,380
Really?

659
00:28:47,250 --> 00:28:48,330
I always thought he was odd.

660
00:28:48,940 --> 00:28:50,050
I must keep an eye on my things.

661
00:28:50,900 --> 00:28:51,620
Indeed.

662
00:28:55,620 --> 00:28:56,220
Are you done?

663
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:57,220
That was quick.

664
00:28:58,050 --> 00:28:59,330
