666
00:29:01,140 --> 00:29:02,810
Qinglai, please clean it up.

667
00:29:02,940 --> 00:29:03,620
Throw it out.

668
00:29:04,900 --> 00:29:05,660
I'm done as well.

669
00:29:06,330 --> 00:29:06,860
Xue.

670
00:29:16,860 --> 00:29:17,570
Throw this out as well.

671
00:29:20,050 --> 00:29:21,180
This one too. Thank you.

672
00:29:21,570 --> 00:29:22,140
Anything else?

673
00:29:22,330 --> 00:29:23,050
-Nope.
-No.

674
00:29:25,660 --> 00:29:26,330
Have a look here.

675
00:29:27,570 --> 00:29:28,090
Qinglai.

676
00:29:28,330 --> 00:29:30,050
Have you seen my Zisha mug?

677
00:29:37,700 --> 00:29:38,530
What do you mean?

678
00:29:39,420 --> 00:29:40,180
I didn't take it.

679
00:29:41,140 --> 00:29:41,330
No.

680
00:29:41,330 --> 00:29:43,180
