691
00:30:12,980 --> 00:30:14,330
Mr. Guan scolded me.

692
00:30:16,900 --> 00:30:18,250
I shall see you out.

693
00:30:18,330 --> 00:30:19,660
-This way, please.
-Okay.

694
00:30:22,380 --> 00:30:23,290
