709
00:31:03,730 --> 00:31:04,620
Xingfu.

710
00:31:05,220 --> 00:31:07,290
I have to be honest. Don't get mad.

711
00:31:08,380 --> 00:31:09,490
I think

712
00:31:10,220 --> 00:31:11,180
