716
00:31:16,180 --> 00:31:17,330
What do you know?

717
00:31:17,860 --> 00:31:18,810
Go back to work.

718
00:31:31,250 --> 00:31:31,980
Gossiping about me?

719
00:31:33,490 --> 00:31:34,490
It was nothing.

720
00:31:38,140 --> 00:31:40,330
Go collect the invoice
for the property management fee.

721
00:31:42,010 --> 00:31:43,180
