00:32:13,660 --> 00:32:15,290
I'm sorry. Let me tidy it up.

726
00:32:21,490 --> 00:32:22,010
What's going on?

727
00:32:24,220 --> 00:32:24,980
Give her a plaster, please.

728
00:32:25,770 --> 00:32:26,050
It's okay.

729
00:32:26,050 --> 00:32:26,530
Do you have plasters?

730
00:32:26,530 --> 00:32:27,010
It's okay.

731
00:32:27,090 --> 00:32:27,460
Oh, my.

732
00:32:27,620 --> 00:32:28,620
Just a small cut.

733
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:30,250
-Don't touch.
-Thank you.

734
00:32:30,420 --> 00:32:31,140
I'll just wipe it off.

735
00:32:31,940 --> 00:32:33,290
Don't squad there. Get up.

736
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:34,180
It's okay.

737
00:32:40,700 --> 00:32:41,050
So?

738
00:32:41,050 --> 00:32:42,290
Is there glass left in your wound?

739
00:32:42,420 --> 00:32:42,810
What?

740
00:32:42,810 --> 00:32:43,260
No.

741
00:32:43,460 --> 00:32:44,130
Show me.

742
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:46,500
Just a small cut. It's okay.

743
00:32:46,500 --> 00:32:47,610
[Fangyuan Law Firm]
Come on.

744
00:32:48,130 --> 00:32:48,980
Give me your hand. Don't move.

745
00:32:48,980 --> 00:32:50,610
I'm really fine.

746
00:32:51,130 --> 00:32:52,260
What fine?

747
00:32:52,420 --> 00:32:53,180
If this goes on,

748
00:32:53,530 --> 00:32:55,420
we'll need a first aid kit in the office.

749
00:32:56,660 --> 00:32:58,130
Stop kidding around.

750
00:32:58,660 --> 00:33:00,330
My hand isn't broken.

751
00:33:00,900 --> 00:33:01,290
Don't move.

752
00:33:02,220 --> 00:33:03,420
It's just a small cut.

753
00:33:03,570 --> 00:33:04,330
Thank you.

754
00:33:04,660 --> 00:33:05,660
I'm really fine.

755
00:33:06,220 --> 00:33:07,900
Stop it. Let Qinglai do it.

756
00:33:08,330 --> 00:33:08,900
Just leave it.

757
00:33:08,900 --> 00:33:10,020
Let go.

758
00:33:16,570 --> 00:33:17,090
Time for food.

759
00:33:20,810 --> 00:33:21,500
Time for food.

760
00:33:23,260 --> 00:33:24,610
Don't always pull a long face

761
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:26,220
as if someone owes you money.

762
00:33:27,220 --> 00:33:29,420
Time passes whether you're happy or not.

763
00:33:29,700 --> 00:33:31,260
Why don't you be happier?

764
00:33:31,850 --> 00:33:33,050
What is there to be happy about?

765
00:33:33,980 --> 00:33:35,330
What is there to be unhappy about?

766
00:33:38,020 --> 00:33:39,260
Would you be happy

767
00:33:39,260 --> 00:33:40,180
if people think you're a thief?

768
00:33:40,810 --> 00:33:42,330
Who thinks you're a thief?

769
00:33:43,130 --> 00:33:44,290
You're too sensitive.

770
00:33:45,740 --> 00:33:47,940
Be more mindful about ordering lunch

771
00:33:47,940 --> 00:33:48,900
and washing the glasses.

772
00:33:49,090 --> 00:33:50,180
I can no longer help you.

773
00:33:50,660 --> 00:33:51,460
Guan Tao said

774
00:33:51,700 --> 00:33:52,570
it was not right.

775
00:33:56,330 --> 00:33:57,180
Did you hear me?

776
00:33:57,330 --> 00:33:58,220
I heard you.

777
00:33:59,180 --> 00:34:00,530
Guan Tao.

778
00:34:01,290 --> 00:34:02,330
How nice.

779
00:34:03,090 --> 00:34:04,050
What's wrong with calling him Guan Tao?

780
00:34:05,130 --> 00:34:06,290
Everyone else calls him Mr. Guan.

781
00:34:06,900 --> 00:34:08,090
Only you call him by his name.

782
00:34:09,250 --> 00:34:10,610
They're really right about you.

783
00:34:10,610 --> 00:34:12,210
You're just being paranoid.

784
00:34:15,900 --> 00:34:16,530
I know

785
00:34:16,940 --> 00:34:18,730
you feel wronged

786
00:34:19,020 --> 00:34:20,210
because they said that you stole plants.

787
00:34:21,170 --> 00:34:22,730
The countryside and the city

788
00:34:23,090 --> 00:34:24,530
have different rules.

789
00:34:24,940 --> 00:34:26,050
Since we're in the city,

790
00:34:26,420 --> 00:34:27,780
we have to follow the rules here.

791
00:34:28,420 --> 00:34:29,690
You know all these.

792
00:34:29,690 --> 00:34:31,170
Why are you being stubborn?

793
00:34:31,650 --> 00:34:32,210
Besides,

794
00:34:32,610 --> 00:34:34,170
since we're receiving salaries,

795
00:34:34,380 --> 00:34:35,980
we have to get our work done properly.

796
00:34:36,300 --> 00:34:37,050
Remember,

797
00:34:37,300 --> 00:34:38,820
we don't work for plants,

798
00:34:38,820 --> 00:34:40,300
we work for people.

799
00:34:41,340 --> 00:34:42,170
Do you know what you did?

800
00:34:42,530 --> 00:34:43,460
The printer was out of ink.

801
00:34:43,460 --> 00:34:44,460
I told you to buy a toner

802
00:34:44,530 --> 00:34:46,020
and it took you half a day.

803
00:34:46,570 --> 00:34:47,780
Mr. Guan needed a document urgently

804
00:34:48,090 --> 00:34:49,380
and I had to go out

805
00:34:49,460 --> 00:34:50,530
to print it at my expense.

806
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:52,380
Luckily, Mr. Guan is nice.

807
00:34:52,690 --> 00:34:54,300
If you were in another company,

808
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:55,380
with your attitude,

809
00:34:55,380 --> 00:34:56,250
you would have been fired.

810
00:34:56,340 --> 00:34:57,050
Fire me then.

811
00:34:58,170 --> 00:34:59,050
I've been meaning to quit.

812
00:34:59,940 --> 00:35:01,820
I have to serve others in the firm

813
00:35:02,900 --> 00:35:04,020
and then come back to be scolded by you.

814
00:35:05,050 --> 00:35:05,690
He Xingfu.

815
00:35:06,820 --> 00:35:07,860
I'm your husband.

816
00:35:07,860 --> 00:35:08,980
Not your child.

817
00:35:12,530 --> 00:35:14,250
You're wrong yet I can't say anything?

818
00:35:15,900 --> 00:35:17,730
Are you saying this because I was wrong?

819
00:35:18,420 --> 00:35:20,050
Or is it because you think I embarrassed you?

820
00:35:20,530 --> 00:35:21,730
I know you're the receptionist.

821
00:35:22,460 --> 00:35:23,500
The hero.

822
00:35:23,530 --> 00:35:24,900
You're looking down on me now.

823
00:35:25,050 --> 00:35:25,980
Who do you prefer now?

824
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:27,530
Guan Tao, right?

825
00:35:28,860 --> 00:35:30,340
The two of you always flirt

826
00:35:30,340 --> 00:35:31,020
in front of me.

827
00:35:31,020 --> 00:35:32,130
Do you think I'm blind?

828
00:35:32,650 --> 00:35:33,340
Besides,

829
00:35:33,460 --> 00:35:34,020
do you really think

830
00:35:34,020 --> 00:35:35,460
you're a true city folk

831
00:35:35,610 --> 00:35:36,860
just because you dress like them?

832
00:35:37,460 --> 00:35:39,130
Do you know what others think about you?

833
00:35:39,130 --> 00:35:39,940
Shut up!

834
00:35:45,380 --> 00:35:46,340
Do you know what you are talking about?

835
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:49,300
He Xingfu.

836
00:35:51,820 --> 00:35:52,940
How dare you hit me?

837
00:35:58,420 --> 00:35:59,340
I can't go on like this anymore!

838
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:02,690
What are you talking about?

839
00:36:03,940 --> 00:36:04,570
I can't go on like this.

840
00:36:04,570 --> 00:36:05,210
Let's get a divorce!

841
00:36:06,860 --> 00:36:07,690
I'm done with this.

842
00:36:09,860 --> 00:36:10,460
I'm done.

843
00:36:18,980 --> 00:36:19,650
You wanted this.

844
00:36:28,900 --> 00:36:29,940
Don't regret it.

845
00:37:14,980 --> 00:37:16,900
[Five-grain pancakes]

846
00:40:20,730 --> 00:40:21,820
Qinglai.

847
00:40:21,980 --> 00:40:23,050
Please come over here.

848
00:40:23,250 --> 00:40:23,650
Okay.

849
00:40:25,570 --> 00:40:26,300
Over here.

850
00:40:30,130 --> 00:40:30,940
This is for this.

