00:40:42,820 --> 00:40:43,250
Hurry up.

856
00:40:43,250 --> 00:40:44,020
Hold on a second.

857
00:40:44,130 --> 00:40:44,650
Okay.

858
00:40:44,940 --> 00:40:45,340
I'll be right back.

859
00:40:46,170 --> 00:40:47,020
Where?

860
00:40:48,170 --> 00:40:49,340
Which address is this?

861
00:40:49,860 --> 00:40:51,210
Hurry. I have more parcels downstairs.

862
00:40:51,340 --> 00:40:53,130
Okay. I'm coming soon.

863
00:41:04,250 --> 00:41:05,460
Take a look. Is this what you want?

864
00:41:05,530 --> 00:41:06,090
Coffee.

865
00:41:06,690 --> 00:41:06,940
Is it right?

866
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:07,610
-Yes.
-Okay, thank you.

867
00:41:07,610 --> 00:41:08,900
-Put it here.
-No worries.

868
00:41:13,610 --> 00:41:14,300
This is yours.

869
00:41:14,780 --> 00:41:15,380
Thank you.

870
00:41:20,610 --> 00:41:21,170
Qinglai.

871
00:41:21,650 --> 00:41:22,210
Great timing. Here.

